article_id:1557,category_name:News,title_name:A New Summon Showcase, Shadow Focus, Is Now Live!,image_path:,message:<div>A Summon Showcase, Shadow Focus, went live <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1599458400"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>In the Shadow Focus summon showcase, only shadow-attuned adventurers and dragons will appear.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Note: The roster for this summon showcase does not include adventurers and dragons that are attuned to elements other than shadow.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Availability period for featured summons:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1599458400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1599890399"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at some of the 5★ adventurers and 5★ dragons who may appear in the Shadow Focus summon showcase.</div><div><br></div><div>5★ adventurers:</div><div>
<div class="summonPickUp">
