				<div class="title">Adventurer Details</div>
				<div class="param">
					<ul>
						<li>One of the apostles of the northern Ilian Church.<br>Though he normally adopts a lackadaisical<br>demeanor, he possesses keen insight and excels<br>in battlefield strategy. He has formed a Sigil with<br>the angel Ramiel, and looks to him like a father.</li>
