		</div></div><div class="skill explanation">
	<div class="title">Skills</div>
	<dl><dt
				>
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/c8617d88f15afc0758a831a32f276e572.png"></span>
				<span>Victoria Strategy</span>
			</dt>
			<dd>
				<div>
					Creates a buff zone that lasts for 10 seconds<br>and increases the strength of shadow-attuned<br>adventurers inside it by 25%. During Sigil Released,<br>this skill also reduces light damage taken by the<br>entire team by 20% for 10 seconds.<br>This damage reduction effect will not stack.
				</div>
			</dd>
	<dt class="skill-cost-wrap"
				>
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/48ad4816ddb1b05918d1b08ce53e562f2.png"></span>
				<span>Magnus Apocalypse</span>
